name: Star Force
overview: A space shoot-em up that was re-released by ECP in 1987. "It looks like another lazy Saturday afternoon", you think as you lazily press the long range scan button. JUMPING ZYLONS!! Four enemy craft penetrating Quadrant 1. You fire up your turbos and warp to Quadrant 1 with your lasers at full power. The battle is on!!!
publishers: ECP (Entertainment and Computer Products Pty. Ltd.)
